            {"II.", "FIELDING",    "Play an Ace or King to summon a spirit onto your Base Cell. Press [F] as a shortcut."},
            {"III.","MOVEMENT",    "Spirits advance clockwise. A Four card moves backward 4 steps. A Five card moves any spirit."},
